Test steps:
1. Verify menu button is visible and clickable
2. Verify expandera under meny (index 1) is visible and clickable
3. Verify expandera under meny (index 3) is visible and clickable

5. Verify låna ut menu item is visible and clickable
6. Verify navigation to låna ut URL
